#originalTopic=should-the-us-have-universal-healthcare
The only person who would ever invoke "having to wait" as a reason to reject   universal health care   is someone who is wealthy enough to get access at all! Given the choice between waiting for care or not having care at all, I'm sure most people would choose the former!Signed,  a proud and grateful and healthy Canadian